*{{IPA|/vɜː(r)b/}}
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /v3:(r)b/

===Noun===
'''verb''' (''plural:'' '''verbs''')

#{{grammar}} a word that indicates an action or a state; in a sentence, a verb forms part of the [[predicate]] of any one sentence.

